  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Game</h2>Brave Heroes is a game where you can play with different heroes with different move abilities and try to complete 4 seasons total of 20 minutes, with the powerful abilities and the help of the environment and nature.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discord Channel</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Abilities</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073970/extras/cc9a10e3de1cdd6c02c93dc2719e40ae.poster.avif?t=1664741842\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073970/extras/cc9a10e3de1cdd6c02c93dc2719e40ae.webm?t=1664741842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073970/extras/cc9a10e3de1cdd6c02c93dc2719e40ae.mp4?t=1664741842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unique abilities to use against thousands of creatures<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Environment</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073970/extras/e254e41fdb1961f917f722fb54becce1.poster.avif?t=1664741842\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073970/extras/e254e41fdb1961f917f722fb54becce1.webm?t=1664741842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073970/extras/e254e41fdb1961f917f722fb54becce1.mp4?t=1664741842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Animals and other materials create areas that give you temporary buffs<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Abilities</h2>Each hero has a different ability<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Necromancer summons skeletons<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shar